social_posts.post_text: Don’t miss your chance for 35% off this holiday season! Visit our website or the boutique in person to claim yours today. 🌟🎁

One of the very first photos of when the Boutique was complete.

Opening up during a pandemic to say it was stressful is an understatement, needless to say our Grand Opening never happened.  We had a soft opening with our current clients exclusive & VIPs only. If you knew then you knew. And we thank you. For being patient as we transitioned into our new home, Naturally by The Boutique, our Sanctuary. 

To our clients thank you for being patient & understanding. We may not be perfect with our annoying software system errors but we promise you, you will leave with great brows, skin, lashes and definitely with a smile. Personally I take pride in creating a space where clients feel so comfortable. And when I hear our clients (whom most are like family) say they want to be at the Boutique all day everyday because it has a "good vibe good energy" it makes my soul smile & gives me faith that reminds me I'm exactly where I should be🙏

We thank you for all the love and support because we couldn't be on this journey without each and every one of you 🤍

To the girls, I hope you know I appreciate, love, respect and want the best for you!  Thank you for joining me on this journey, our energy at the Boutique is beautiful because all of you. Looking forward to creating many more memories together ✨

Photos by @_abimages @alexberliner

Wait why wasn’t I getting lash lifts ages ago …. @savannahsbeautybar @savannahbree is my queen angel lover i am getting these every 8 weeks for the rest of my life wow ❤️ she’s at @naturallyby in beverly hills !!!

🤍 Happiest Holidays 🤍

May we all learn to choose love, and appreciate what we have. Health, family, friends...to never loose sight of our dreams, and continue to manifest the life we all deserve. 

2022 was an insane year for us as a family. I started a beauty business in a pandemic, as you all know!  My husband also started his own business. Add in a VERY ACTIVE, INQUISITIVE, 4-year old, who BEATS TO HIS OWN DRUM, it's been a wild year! 

Love to you always, 
Stevi + Family

I didn't think I had very many 2022 highlights, it was a tough year to say the least.  Yet, as I focused on the business I realized there were VERY MANY grateful moments I should share. 

Our VIP Opening Event Feb 10th. Adding Four incredible employees in March. Then another talented employee. Clients whom become friends. A fab Mothers Day event. Red Carpet Events with talented artists who I LOVE having at the boutique. To Bday Celebrations. Last Minute Photoshoots. Our Boutique Ladies Night. To Holidays. To getting ready for Our New Year together. 

To all the girls, I love and appreciate you. We have such a beautiful energy at The Boutique that I've always wanted to create. And I couldn't do it without you all! I'm excited to create many more memories & add more Naturally By services to the Menu 🤍

Stay Tuned we have a lot in store for you, 2023! ✨

Xx, Stevi

MONDAY MOTIVATION

MAKE YOURSELF A PRIORITY. Self care is an important element in life. It's not selfish. We all need to love ourselves a bit more. As simple as going for a walk, getting a massage and/or a facial/beauty treatments, meditating (it's my new thing), meeting up with family/friends etc., doing the things that make YOU happy! 🤍

Love always, Stevi
